    <abstract id="aspace_49885adc1588eff641b8a35c9a16211b">This collection documents early Colonial property transactions in the Long Island towns of Brookhaven and Southold. Materials include deeds, indentures, patents and warrents, and involve the Unkechaug Native Americans and English colonial administrator Edmund Andros.</abstract>
